instructions: Put the plate on the charger
Put the napkin on top of the plate oriented vertically
Put the dinner fork to the left on the charger with the prongs facing up
Put the salad fork to the left on the dinner fork with the tongs facing up
Put the dinner knife to the right of the charger with the blade facing left
Put the teaspoon to the right of the dinner knife with the bowl facing up
Put the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon with the bowl facing up
Put the water glass above the charger to the left of the dinner knife and right of the charger
Put the wine class to the right of the water glass, between the tea spoon and the soup spoon
Put the wine class below the other wine glass, above the tea spoon
Put the coffee cup to the right of the lower wine glass above and right of the soup spoon
Put the bread plate above the two forks
Put the butter knife on the bread plate with the blade facing left
Put the dessert fork above the charger with the prongs facing right
Put the dessert spook below the dessert fork above the charger with the bowl facing left
